                    h3 Passion Project
                    p I wanted to put a little flavor in here with some personal work. No business or user goals other than just to bring creatives together from around the globe to make some really incredible collaborative works in Lubomierz, Poland. The event has gained the small hosting town international attention.

                    h6 Metroid Team ( 1 / 15 )
                    ul
                        li Creative Team Lead: Chris Norton
                        li Talent / Costume Fabrication: Willow Creative (Netherlands)
                        li Assistant: Katharine Repetski
                        li Location Scout / Manager: Ambroży Kleks

